variables; number; sum; counter

sum = sum + number
counter = 0

process;
step 1; input a number;
check if the number is integer;
if yes go to step 2; if no; print "this is not a valid number"

step 2; add 1 to counter and go to step 3

step 3; if counter is smaller than 100 go to step 1; 
if counter is equal to 100 go to step 4

step 4; print sum 
